To exclude the parsing part from the benchmarks, I usually parse the triples directly into an ArrayList first:
```
public List<Triple> readTriples(String graphUri) {
        var list = new ArrayList<Triple>();
        var g1 = new GraphMem() {
            @Override
            public void add(Triple t) {
                list.add(t);
            }
        };
        RDFDataMgr.read(g1, graphUri);
        return list;
    }
```
